425, \"to\": 620, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 449, \"end\": 459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Jones-Hall\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.671748790357233e-13, \"text\": \"Jade Jones\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Jones-Hall\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Jones-Hall\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 447}, {\"ngram\": \"performance-enhancing drugs\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 514}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic taekwondo\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 564}, {\"ngram\": \"an anti-doping testin December\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 31-year-old, who won Olympic gold medals in London and Rio de Janeiro, was cleared of fault by the UK Anti-Doping Agency (Ukad) in a verdict issued shortly before the Games, after she presented an unspecified medical condition in mitigation.\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 867, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 670, \"end\": 676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999998835847, \"rank\": 1.0975668666443764e-10, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 681, \"end\": 695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.281414579590776e-17, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 725, \"end\": 739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Anti-Doping\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Anti-Doping\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Anti-Doping\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Anti-Doping\"}, {\"begin\": 725, \"end\": 739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Anti-Doping\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Anti-Doping\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Anti-Doping\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Anti-Doping\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic gold medals\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 666}, {\"ngram\": \"fault\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 717}, {\"ngram\": \"Ukad\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 752}, {\"ngram\": \"a verdict\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 766}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 798}, {\"ngram\": \"an unspecified medical condition\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 852}, {\"ngram\": \"mitigation\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 866}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Grand Palais in Paris, the No 3-ranked Jones suffered a surprise opening-round defeat by Miljana Reljikj of North Macedonia to end her hopes of winning a third Olympic title.\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 1050, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 892, \"end\": 897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999731699, \"rank\": 2.699805730972527e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Grand Palais\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 888}, {\"ngram\": \"the No 3-ranked Jones\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 920}, {\"ngram\": \"a surprise opening-round defeat\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 961}, {\"ngram\": \"Miljana Reljikj\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 980}, {\"ngram\": \"North Macedonia\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"her hopes\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1016}, {\"ngram\": \"a third Olympic title\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The best-of-three bout went to a deciding round, which was drawn 1-1, but Reljikj won the contest by virtue of being the more aggressive fighter.\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1196, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The best-of-three bout\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1073}, {\"ngram\": \"a deciding round\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1098}, {\"ngram\": \"Reljikj\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"the contest\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"virtue\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1158}, {\"ngram\": \"the more aggressive fighter\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1195}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Afterwards a clearly emotional Jones said she has always been a clean competitor.\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1279, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a clearly emotional Jones\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1234}, {\"ngram\": \"a clean competitor\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"No, I can confirm I have never taken drugs,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1336, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"drugs\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1324}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have done hundreds of tests.\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1368, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hundreds\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"tests\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1367}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since then I have done I think 13 more tests, blood, and I have never had any [positive results].\\\"\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1467, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"13 more tests\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"blood\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1420}, {\"ngram\": \"any [positive results\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1464}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added: \\\"I am obviously not on drugs, I just lost.\\\"\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1523, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"drugs\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1508}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Had she been found at fault by Ukad, Jones risked a long-term suspension from the sport.\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1613, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fault\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1552}, {\"ngram\": \"Ukad\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1560}, {\"ngram\": \"Jones\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1567}, {\"ngram\": \"a long-term suspension\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1597}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1603, \"to\": 1612}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was not the sort of missed test which can occasionally happen when an athlete fails to fill in their whereabouts online and is not home when a tester calls by.\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1778, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sort\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1635}, {\"ngram\": \"missed test\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1650}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1696}, {\"ngram\": \"their whereabouts\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"a tester\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1768}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes can make two whereabouts failures in 12 months before the third triggers a violation and potential ban.\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"two whereabouts failures\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1821}, {\"ngram\": \"12 months\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1834}, {\"ngram\": \"a violation\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1872}, {\"ngram\": \"potential ban\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, when Jones was approached by a doping control officer at a Manchester hotel at 7am on 1 December last year, she refused to take the test.\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 2039, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jones\", \"from\": 1907, \"to\": 1912}, {\"ngram\": \"a doping control officer\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1955}, {\"ngram\": \"a Manchester hotel\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1977}, {\"ngram\": \"1 December\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 1998}, {\"ngram\": \"the test\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2038}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jones explained to the doping control officer that she could not offer up a urine sample because she had not eaten or drunk anything for two days in an effort to make a weigh-in that morning.\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2232, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jones\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2046}, {\"ngram\": \"the doping control officer\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2086}, {\"ngram\": \"a urine sample\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2129}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2173}, {\"ngram\": \"two days\", \"from\": 2178, \"to\": 2186}, {\"ngram\": \"an effort\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2199}, {\"ngram\": \"a weigh\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2215}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to the case report, the doping control officer reminded Jones \\\"approximately five times\\\" of the potentially serious anti-doping violation she risked committing by failing to comply, which carries a ban of up to four years.\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2466, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the case report\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2262}, {\"ngram\": \"the doping control officer\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2290}, {\"ngram\": \"Jones\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2305}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"approximately five times\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2331}, {\"ngram\": \"the potentially serious anti-doping violation\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2381}, {\"ngram\": \"a ban\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2445}, {\"ngram\": \"up to four years\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2465}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Jones signed a form indicating she could not provide a sample.\", \"from\": 2467, \"to\": 2533, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jones\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2476}, {\"ngram\": \"a form\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2490}, {\"ngram\": \"a sample\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I signed a piece of paper, yeah,\\\" she explained.\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a piece\", \"from\": 2545, \"to\": 2552}, {\"ngram\": \"paper\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I did not know what I was signing.\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2624, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was fully dehydrated.\", \"from\": 2625, \"to\": 2648, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I had not drank and wasn't in the right mind to sign it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2706, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right mind\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2693}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around an hour later, she left the hotel alone to go home before the weigh-in.\", \"from\": 2708, \"to\": 2786, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hotel\", \"from\": 2739, \"to\": 2748}, {\"ngram\": \"the weigh-in\", \"from\": 2773, \"to\": 2785}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jones did then give a sample to a different doping control officer later that evening, which was clean.\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jones\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2793}, {\"ngram\": \"a sample\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2816}, {\"ngram\": \"a different doping control officer\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2854}, {\"ngram\": \"later that evening\", \"from\": 2855, \"to\": 2873}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that was 12 hours later, a window in which some substances can become undetectable.\", \"from\": 2892, \"to\": 2979, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some substances\", \"from\": 2939, \"to\": 2954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The drugs tester's come on dehydration day,\\\" Jones explained.\", \"from\": 2981, \"to\": 3043, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"dehydration day\", \"from\": 3009, \"to\": 3024}, {\"ngram\": \"Jones\", \"from\": 3027, \"to\": 3032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And, people who know, when you are losing the weight, you have not eaten and drank for a few days.\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3143, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3050, \"to\": 3056}, {\"ngram\": \"the weight\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3097}, {\"ngram\": \"a few days\", \"from\": 3132, \"to\": 3142}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I said straight away, 'Let us go, you have to come with me [to a dehydration bath], I have got to lose the weight'.\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3263, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3175, \"to\": 3177}, {\"ngram\": \"a dehydration bath\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3229}, {\"ngram\": \"the weight\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Then, basically, she did not know if she could come or not.\", \"from\": 3265, \"to\": 3325, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So there was a lot of stress, and I was waiting.\", \"from\": 3326, \"to\": 3374, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3339, \"to\": 3344}, {\"ngram\": \"stress\", \"from\": 3348, \"to\": 3354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I needed to go and dehydrate and weigh in.\", \"from\": 3375, \"to\": 3417, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I became stressed.\", \"from\": 3418, \"to\": 3436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I wasn't in the right mind.\", \"from\": 3437, \"to\": 3464, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right mind\", \"from\": 3449, \"to\": 3463}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And basically I thought you could miss three [tests].\", \"from\": 3465, \"to\": 3518, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"three [tests\", \"from\": 3504, \"to\": 3516}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I was very lucky, they looked into it, seen I wasn't in the wrong.\\\"\", \"from\": 3519, \"to\": 3589, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wrong\", \"from\": 3578, \"to\": 3587}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After a drawn-out disciplinary process, the UK Anti-Doping Agency (Ukad) passed a 'no-fault' ruling on the basis of a report by a psychiatrist, which concluded that Jones's \\\"decision to refuse or failure to provide a sample occurred as a direct result of her cognitive impairment\\\".\", \"from\": 3591, \"to\": 3872, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3635, \"end\": 3649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Anti-Doping\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Anti-Doping\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Anti-Doping\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Anti-Doping\"}, {\"begin\": 3635, \"end\": 3649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Anti-Doping\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Anti-Doping\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Anti-Doping\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Anti-Doping\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a drawn-out disciplinary process\", \"from\": 3597, \"to\": 3629}, {\"ngram\": \"Ukad\", \"from\": 3658, \"to\": 3662}, {\"ngram\": \"a 'no-fault' ruling\", \"from\": 3671, \"to\": 3690}, {\"ngram\": \"the basis\", \"from\": 3694, \"to\": 3703}, {\"ngram\": \"a report\", \"from\": 3707, \"to\": 3715}, {\"ngram\": \"a psychiatrist\", \"from\": 3719, \"to\": 3733}, {\"ngram\": \"Jones's \\\"decision\", \"from\": 3756, \"to\": 3773}, {\"ngram\": \"a sample\", \"from\": 3806, \"to\": 3814}, {\"ngram\": \"a direct result\", \"from\": 3827, \"to\": 3842}, {\"ngram\": \"her cognitive impairment\", \"from\": 3846, \"to\": 3870}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The details of Jones's medical condition have been kept confidential, but Ukad said the verdict was a result of \\\"very exceptional circumstances\\\".\", \"from\": 3874, \"to\": 4019, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The details\", \"from\": 3874, \"to\": 3885}, {\"ngram\": \"Jones's medical condition\", \"from\": 3889, \"to\": 3914}, {\"ngram\": \"Ukad\", \"from\": 3948, \"to\": 3952}, {\"ngram\": \"the verdict\", \"from\": 3958, \"to\": 3969}, {\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 3974, \"to\": 3982}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"very exceptional circumstances\", \"from\": 3986, \"to\": 4017}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jones did not speak to the media in the build-up to the Games.\", \"from\": 4021, \"to\": 4083, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jones\", \"from\": 4021, \"to\": 4026}, {\"ngram\": \"the media\", \"from\": 4044, \"to\": 4053}, {\"ngram\": \"the build-up\", \"from\": 4057, \"to\": 4069}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 4073, \"to\": 4082}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She released only a brief statement, saying she was \\\"stressed and panicked\\\" by her weigh-in when the doping control officer arrived.\", \"from\": 4084, \"to\": 4216, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only a brief statement\", \"from\": 4097, \"to\": 4119}, {\"ngram\": \"her weigh-in\", \"from\": 4163, \"to\": 4175}, {\"ngram\": \"the doping control officer\", \"from\": 4181, \"to\": 4207}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here she fronted up after a difficult day, having gone out at the first hurdle just as she did in Tokyo three years earlier.\", \"from\": 4218, \"to\": 4342, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4316, \"end\": 4321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9409481611360604, \"rank\": 0.06275764427893486, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a difficult day\", \"from\": 4244, \"to\": 4259}, {\"ngram\": \"the first hurdle\", \"from\": 4280, \"to\": 4296}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Right now it's pretty hard, but I am super proud of having the courage to try to do something that no one's done [win three golds].\", \"from\": 4344, \"to\": 4476, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the courage\", \"from\": 4404, \"to\": 4415}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 4429, \"to\": 4438}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 4444, \"to\": 4450}, {\"ngram\": \"three golds\", \"from\": 4463, \"to\": 4474}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The more you win, the harder it gets, the pressure, the mental side of it, and it's just tough.\", \"from\": 4477, \"to\": 4572, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 4515, \"to\": 4527}, {\"ngram\": \"the mental side\", \"from\": 4529, \"to\": 4544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I came out today and I froze and did not have the balls that it took to fight free, let my legs go.\", \"from\": 4574, \"to\": 4674, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the balls\", \"from\": 4621, \"to\": 4630}, {\"ngram\": \"my legs\", \"from\": 4663, \"to\": 4670}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just gutted that I did not show what I was capable of, that me and my coach have worked so hard to show.\", \"from\": 4675, \"to\": 4784, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my coach\", \"from\": 4747, \"to\": 4755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If anything, that's the biggest regret.\\\"\", \"from\": 4785, \"to\": 4825, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the biggest regret\", \"from\": 4805, \"to\": 4823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked what the future holds, Jones said: \\\"I do not know yet, I am not sure.\", \"from\": 4827, \"to\": 4902, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 4838, \"to\": 4848}, {\"ngram\": \"Jones\", \"from\": 4856, \"to\": 4861}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will just go back home, see my family, and see what happens.\\\"\", \"from\": 4903, \"to\": 4966, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my family\", \"from\": 4933, \"to\": 4942}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 4968, \"to\": 5198, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5019, \"end\": 5030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.289354017831893e-17, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thought-provoking conversations\", \"from\": 4973, \"to\": 5004}, {\"ngram\": \"their replies\", \"from\": 5047, \"to\": 5060}, {\"ngram\": \"the page\", \"from\": 5076, \"to\": 5084}, {\"ngram\": \"another page\", \"from\": 5100, \"to\": 5112}, {\"ngram\": \"the site\", \"from\": 5116, \"to\": 5124}, {\"ngram\": \"inPlease\", \"from\": 5152, \"to\": 5160}, {\"ngram\": \"your browser\", \"from\": 5169, \"to\": 5181}]}]}"